sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User as User Browser (Mock UI)
  participant API as Backend API Service
  participant Score as Score Service
  participant RT as Realtime Hub (SSE)

  User->>API: GET /api/v1/leaderboard?limit=10 (API key)
  API->>Score: getTopLeaderboard(10)
  Score-->>API: top10 snapshot
  API-->>User: success envelope with leaderboard data

  User->>API: POST /api/v1/actions/complete { userId, actionId, actionProof }
  API->>API: Validate API key + action proof
  API->>Score: applyActionScore(userId, actionId, +10)
  Score-->>API: { applied, score }
  API->>Score: getTopLeaderboard(10)
  Score-->>API: updated top10
  API->>RT: broadcast leaderboard.updated
  RT-->>User: SSE event leaderboard.updated
  API-->>User: success envelope for action completion
